<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,152,554]" box="[198,1304,490,516]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,275,490,516]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Notes.</emphasis>
The species differs from all other known Chinese species by the remarkably small size.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
